{"html": [{"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; ESTABLECE FUNCIONAMIENTO DE JUNTAS INSCRIPTORAS N&#xFA;m. O-403.- Santiago, 14 de Febrero de 1996.- Vistos:</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 1.- La necesidad de facilitar las labores de las Juntas Inscriptoras que se indican en la parte resolutiva.</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 2. Las facultades que me confiere el Art. 93&#xB0; en sus letras i) y k) de la Ley N&#xB0; 18.556, Ley Org&#xE1;nica Constitucional sobre Sistema de Inscripciones Electorales y Servicio Electoral,</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; Resuelvo:</div><br></div>", "i": 6010062}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; Establ&#xE9;cese que las Juntas Inscriptoras que a continuaci&#xF3;n se se&#xF1;alan, funcionar&#xE1;n durante el a&#xF1;o 1996, en los per&#xED;odos dispuestos en el Art. 35&#xB0; de la Ley N&#xB0; 18.556:</div><div class=\"p\"> I Regi&#xF3;n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; :&nbsp; Chiapa</div><div class=\"p\"> VI Regi&#xF3;n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  :&nbsp; San Pedro de Alc&#xE1;ntara y Pelequ&#xE9;n</div><div class=\"p\"> VII Regi&#xF3;n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; :&nbsp; Toconey y La Huerta.</div><div class=\"p\"> VIII Regi&#xF3;n&nbsp; &nbsp;  :&nbsp; Isla Mocha, Isla Santa Mar&#xED;a y</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Campanario.</div><div class=\"p\"> IX Regi&#xF3;n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  :&nbsp; Nehuentu&#xE9;, Huiscapi, Lican-Ray,</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Radal, Quepe, Hualp&#xED;n y Queule.</div><div class=\"p\"> X Regi&#xF3;n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; :&nbsp; Malalhue, Ayacara, Peulla,</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Mechuque, Chaulinec, Quenac, Colaco,</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Isla Guar, Llanada Grande, Riachuelo,</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Ca&#xF1;itas, Misi&#xF3;n de la Costa,</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Carelmapu, Hueyusca, Pargua, Ril&#xE1;n,</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Isla Puluqui, Mehu&#xED;n, Isla Maillen,</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Tegualda, Antilhue, Metahue,</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Hualaihu&#xE9; Puerto y Tena&#xFA;n.</div><div class=\"p\"> XI Regi&#xF3;n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  :&nbsp; Bah&#xED;a Murta, Ma&#xF1;ihuales, Corcovado</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; y La Tapera.</div><div class=\"p\"> XII Regi&#xF3;n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; :&nbsp;  Puerto Ed&#xE9;n.</div><br></div>", "i": 6010063}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; An&#xF3;tese, comun&#xED;quese y publ&#xED;quese.- Juan Ignacio Garc&#xED;a Rodr&#xED;guez, Director.</div><br></div>", "i": 6010064}], "proyectos": [], "otrosSistemas": [], "jurisprudencia": [], "doctrina": [], "metadatos": {"tiene_notas": false, "tipos_numeros": [{"tipo": "3", "numero": "403", "abreviacion": "RES", "descripcion": "Resolución", "compuesto": "RES-403"}, {"tipo": "3", "numero": "O-403", "abreviacion": "RES", "descripcion": "Resolución", "compuesto": "RES-O-403"}], "organismos": ["SERVICIO ELECTORAL"], "titulo_norma": "ESTABLECE FUNCIONAMIENTO DE JUNTAS INSCRIPTORAS", "fuente": "Diario Oficial", "resumenes": [], "materias": [], "terminos_libres": ["JUNTA INSCRIPTORA", "SERVICIO ELECTORAL", "CHIAPA", "SAN PEDRO ALCANTARA", "TOCONEY", "ISLA MOCHA", "ISLA SANTA MARIA", "NEHUENTUE", "AYACARA", "PEULLA", "MECHUQUE", "CHAULINEC", "QUENAC", "COLACO", "ISLA GUAR", "LLANADA GRANDE", "CORCOVADO", "LA TAPERA", "PELEQUEN", "LA HUERTA", "CAMPANARIO", "HISCAPI", "LICAN-RAY", "RADAL", "QUEPE", "HUALPIN", "QUEULE", "MALAL